==Personal life==
Wright was born in Ann Arbor, Michigan, in 1969.  She migrated to Australia in 1974 with her mother.  She lives in Melbourne with her husband, furniture designer and craftsman [http://www.wrightstudios.com.au Damien Wright], and their three children.<ref>{{cite web |url =http://thestellaprize.com.au/the-stella-prize/2014-2/ |title =The Forgotten Rebels of Eureka by Clare Wright |last = |first = |date = |work = |publisher =The Stella Prize |accessdate =30 April 2014 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140506061431/http://thestellaprize.com.au/the-stella-prize/2014-2/ |archive-date =6 May 2014 |dead-url =yes }}</ref>

